: rgb(1, 1, 1);\">IEEE TPAMI</span></em></span></span></span><br></p></li><li><p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong>Mar. 1, 2021</strong>,</span><strong> </strong>two papers are accepted by <em>CVPR 2021</em></p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Feb. 5, 2021</span>, one paper is accepted by <em>IEEE TIP</em></p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Jan. 22, 2021</span>, one paper is accepted by <em>Light: Science &amp; Applications</em></p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Jan. 7, 2021</span>, one paper is accepted by <em>Nature Photonics</em></p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Dec. 2, 2020</span>, one paper is accepted by <em>IEEE TPAMI</em></p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Oct. 8, 2020</span>, one paper is accepted by <em>Advances in Optics and Photonics</em></p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Aug. 28, 2020</span>,&nbsp;the 2nd <a href=\"http://www.gigavision.cn/\" target=\"_self\">GigaVision</a> Workshop is held at <em>ECCV 2020</em></p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Aug. 27, 2020</span>, one paper is accepted by <em>IEEE TPAMI</em></p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">July 29, 2020</span>, one paper is accepted by <em>ACM Multimedia 2020</em></p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">July 3, 2020</span>, one paper is accepted as <em>ECCV 2020</em> Spotlight Paper</p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">May 18, 2020</span>, two papers are accepted by <em>IEEE TPAMI</em></p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">May 13, 2020</span>,&nbsp;one paper&nbsp;is accepted by <em>Nature Machine Intelligence</em></p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: